# README.md + download_spero_publications.sh stay tracked.
docs/00_Project_Input/publications/*.pdf
# Extracted text working files
docs/00_Project_Input/publications/_extracted_text/

# Excel/Word owner-lock temp files
~$*

# LibreOffice owner-lock temp files
.~lock.*#
